<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .error-container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #d9534f;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        a {
            color: #31708f;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <h1>Error</h1>
        <p>Sorry, something went wrong. Please try again later.</p>
        <p>If the problem persists, contact <a href="">achivallithode3@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
